briefdescription.para: This API returns back the IP address by the host name.

parameterdescription.para: - The string pointer holding the host name
- The variable in which IP address to be stored
- Error occurred in fetching the ip address

briefdescription.para: This API initializes the PAL modules required by the serval.
Initializes the structure holding socket related parameters.Presently it also creates the task which monitors the sockets.
This will initialize the ServalPAL module and its necessary resources.
